headline: U.S. Bank Marks 25 Years in Europe with Spotlight on Irish Origins, Innovation and Community Leadership
summary: DUBLIN, July 30, 2025--U.S. Bank (NYSE: USB), the fifth-largest commercial bank in the United States, is celebrating 25 years of operations in Europe, a journey that began in Arklow, Ireland and laid the foundations for one of Europe’s leading payment providers, Elavon.
